Como baixar e instalar o Microsoft Office LTSC Professional Plus 2024

Link do nosso Site:
https://idatech.com.br/office-2024-original-e-gratuito/
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Liunks oficiais da Microsoft:

Link 1
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=49117

Link 2
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/deployoffice/preview-ltsc2024/install-ltsc-preview#activate-office-ltsc-preview

----------------------------------------------------------------------
COMANDOS PARA O CMD.:
----------------------------------------------------------------------

1ยบ comando = cd c:\office\

2ยบ comando = setup /download office2024.xml


3ยบ comando = setup /configure office2024.xml



----------------------------------------------------------------------
MODELO DO XML :
----------------------------------------------------------------------

<Configuration>
  <Add OfficeClientEdition="64"  Channel="PerpetualVL2024">
     <Product ID="ProPlus2024Volume" PIDKEY="Y63J7-9RNDJ-GD3BV-BDKBP-HH966" >
	   <Language ID="pt-br" />
        <ExcludeApp ID="Access" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Outlook" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="OneDrive" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="OneNote" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Bing" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Groove" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Publisher" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Teams" />
	<ExcludeApp ID="Lync" />
    </Product>
      </Add>
  <RemoveMSI />
  <Property Name="AUTOACTIVATE" Value="1" />
</Configuration>

